      <li>Misrepresent affiliation with the project, impersonate operators, or spoof bot responses.</li>
      <li>Use automated means to trigger commands in bulk in a way that degrades the service for others.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      We may warn, throttle, block, or remove access (per user, guild, or globally) if we reasonably believe
      you breached these Terms or endangered stability, security, or other users.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Third-party services and content</h2>
